In the swatch panel double click on the
pattern design and pattern edition will be
enabled on your workspace.
With the eyedropper ( ) select the pattern
to set it as a fill.
You can then fill any stroke, object, brush.
This vector graphic is rendered as a PATTERN, which means you can
use it as a fill in any object of any size and it will repeat the pattern
infinitely.
